Pool Strike					KEY:Pool Strike ~ Magus Arcana			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural.MagusArcana																	DEFINE:MagusPoolStrikeDamageDice|0	DESC:You can expend 1 point from your arcane pool as a standard action to charge your free hand with energy. You can make a melee touch attack with that hand as a free action as part of activating this ability. If the touch attack hits, it releases the charge and deals %1d6 points of energy damage (acid, cold, electricity, or fire, chosen when he spends the arcane pool point to activate this ability). You can use this ability with the spellstrike class feature. If you miss with this attack, you can hold the charge for up to 1 minute before it dissipates.|MagusPoolStrikeDamageDice																												BONUS:VAR|MagusPoolStrikeDamageDice|floor(MagusArcanaLVL/3)+1																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.12
Quickened Magic				KEY:Quickened Magic ~ Magus Arcana			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.MagusArcana												PREVARGTEQ:MagusArcanaLVL,15							DESC:You can cast one spell per day as if it were modified by the Quicken Spell feat. This does not increase the level of the spell.																																																																																																																																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.12
Reflection					KEY:Reflection ~ Magus Arcana				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural.MagusArcana												PREVARGTEQ:MagusArcanaLVL,15							DESC:You can sacrifice 1 or more points from your arcane pool as an immediate action to reflect a spell back at its caster. This functions as Spell Turning, but only if the targeted spell is of a level equal to or lower than the number of points expended.  If insufficient points are expended, they instead grant an insight bonus on any saving throws allowed by the spell, equal to the number of points spent.																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.12
Silent Magic				KEY:Silent Magic ~ Magus Arcana			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.MagusArcana																							DESC:You can cast one spell per day as if it were modified by the Silent Spell feat. This does not increase the casting time or the level of the spell.																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.12
#NEEDS CODE/DATA WORK: Not implemented
Spell Blending				KEY:Spell Blending ~ Magus Arcana			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordianry.MagusArcana																							DESC:You select one spell from the wizard spell list that is of a magus spell level you can cast. You add this spell to your spellbook and list of magus spells known as a magus spell of its wizard spell level. You can instead select two spells to add in this way, but both must be at least one level lower than the highest-level magus spell you can cast. You can select this magus arcana more than once.																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.12
Spell Shield				KEY:Spell Shield ~ Magus Arcana			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.MagusArcana																	DEFINE:SpellShieldBonus|0		DESC:You can expend a points from your arcane pool as an immediate action to grant yourself a +%1 shield bonus to AC until the end of your next turn.|SpellShieldBonus																																																																																							BONUS:COMBAT|AC|SpellShieldBonus|TYPE=Shield				BONUS:VAR|SpellShieldBonus|INT																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.12
Still Magic					KEY:Still Magic ~ Magus Arcana			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.MagusArcana																							DESC:You can cast one spell per day as if it were modified by the Still Spell feat. This does not increase the casting time or the level of the spell.																																																																																																																																																						SOURCEPAGE:p.12
Wand Mastery				KEY:Wand Mastery ~ Magus Arcana			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.MagusArcana																							DESC:When you use a wand, you calculates the DC for any spell it contains using your Intelligence modifier, instead of the minimum modifier needed to cast a spell of that level.																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.12
Wand Wielder				KEY:Wand Wielder ~ Magus Arcana			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural.MagusArcana																							DESC:You can activate a wand or staff in place of casting a spell when using spell combat.																																																																																																																																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.12

