Caging Strike	KEY:Caging Strike ~ Imprisonment Domain	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural	DESC:With a devastating weapon strike, spectral chains wrap around your target for a short period of time. Whenever you confirm a critical hit with a melee or ranged weapon attack (including spells that require attack rolls), you can choose to also entangle that target for 1d4 rounds (Fortitude DC %1 negates). You may use this ability %2 times per day.|CagingStrikeDC|DomainImprisonmentTimes	DEFINE:CagingStrikeDC|DomainImprisonmentDC	BONUS:VAR|CagingStrikeDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Caging Strike)	SOURCEPAGE:p.42
