Grasp of Honesty		KEY:Grasp of Honesty ~ Truth Domain		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:Any creature you are grappling or pinning is affected by zone of truth (Will DC %1 negates). Outside of combat, you may use this ability by touching a target with both hands. You can use this ability %2 rounds per day. These rounds do not need to be consecutive. The effect ends if you stop grappling, pinning, or touching the target.|GraspOfHonestyDC|GraspOfHonestyRounds	DEFINE:GraspOfHonestyRounds|DomainTruthLVL	DEFINE:GraspOfHonestyDC|DomainTruthDC	SOURCEPAGE:p.44	BONUS:VAR|GraspOfHonestyDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Grasp of Honesty)

